Introduction

Nina, also known as Song Soowoo, is a South Korean singer under Neo Records.

In 2020, she was named the winner in the teen reality survival show "CAP-TEEN." She went on to debut using her real name Song Soowoo with her digital single "Love Me or Hate Me" on February 3, 2022. After a period of hiatus, she returned to the music industry under the stage name Nina and re-debuted through the digital single "Love Like This on February 14, 2024.
